				<i class="ri-arrow-right-up-line"></i>
			</div>
			<p class="p-0 m-0 leading-none">
				Find more information about getting tickets for public transit
				around Kelowna.
			</p>
			<a class="no-underline p-2 m-0 leading-none border-[1px] rounded-md border-solid border-black hover:cursor-pointer">Learn More</a>
		</div>
		<div class="border-[1px] border-solid border-black rounded-md p-5 flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-4">
			<div class="flex flex-row w-full justify-between items-center">
